A metro police officer has been shot dead on the R102 in Verulam. #DStv403 KWAZULU-NATAL - A metro police officer has been shot dead in Verulam. The off-duty officer was gunned down on the R102 in a suspected assassination. Metro police confirmed the victim as an inspector stationed in Verulam. WATCH: Verulam in shock after three bodies found in house Prem Balram of Reaction Unit South Africa says the victim sustained multiple gun-shot wounds to his body and face. Balram added that it was confirmed that the victim was part-owner of eight taxis and was involved in the taxi industry. Watch the video above for more on this story.